The left bottom panel of Fig. 14 implies that the fallback material and the dynamical ejecta may be considered to be launched from an approximately common periastron. Taking the t-5/3\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
