				\begin{document}$${5}\, {\hbox {ms}}$$\end{document} after the onset of merger for a typical model. This simulation is performed with the LS220 equation of state (Lattimer and Swesty 1991) and a leakage scheme for neutrino emission (but without neutrino absorption).

